      <title>慢慢滑，比較快：SLUGGISH</title>
      <link href="/2026/07/12/sk8/SLUGGISH/"/>
      <url>/2026/07/12/sk8/SLUGGISH/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="介紹"><a href="#介紹" class="headerlink" title="介紹"></a>介紹</h2><p>《SLUGGISH》是一本由比利時布魯塞爾滑板團體SLUGS製作的獨立滑板雜誌外，還是他們發行的第一本Skatezine。雜誌主要記錄女孩、女性與酷兒滑板社群的日常生活，內容除了街頭與滑板場的攝影外，還收錄滑手訪談、插畫與拼貼、<a href="#sluggish-playlist">音樂播放清單</a>、受傷經驗，以及團體舉辦活動和共同建立DIY滑板空間的過程。它並非一本以滑板招式、賽事或職業滑手為主的傳統滑板雜誌，而是從SLUGS自身的社群經驗出發，呈現滑板如何將不同的人聚集在一起，並延伸至藝術創作、音樂、身分認同與社會行動。</p><p>“SLUGGISH” is an independent skateboarding magazine created by the Brussels-based Belgian skate collective SLUGS, marking their first Skatezine publication. The magazine primarily documents the daily lives of girls, women, and queer skateboarding communities. Its content includes photography from street and skatepark scenes, skateboarder interviews, illustrations and collages, music playlists, injury stories, as well as coverage of events organized by the collective and their collaborative efforts in building DIY skate spaces. Unlike traditional skate magazines that focus on tricks, competitions, or professional skaters, “SLUGGISH” draws from SLUGS’ own community experiences to showcase how skateboarding brings diverse people together and extends into artistic expression, music, identity, and social activism.</p><div style="display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: nowrap; align-items: flex-start; margin: 1.5rem auto;">  <figure style="flex: 0 0 calc(50% - 6px); min-width: 0; margin: 0; text-align: center;">    <img      src="/img/sk8/magazine/SLUGGISH1.jpg"      alt="SLUGGISH 封面/Front cover"      style="display: block; width: 100%; height: auto; margin: 0;"    >    <figcaption        class="image-caption"        style="            display: block;            width: 100%;            margin: 0.3rem 0 0;            padding: 0;            font-size: 0.72rem;            line-height: 1.25;            white-space: normal;            overflow-wrap: anywhere;            word-break: break-word;        "    >      圖一、SLUGGISH 封面/Front cover    </figcaption>  </figure>  <figure style="flex: 0 0 calc(50% - 6px); min-width: 0; margin: 0; text-align: center;">    <img      src="/img/sk8/magazine/SLUGGISH2.jpg"      alt="SLUGGISH 封底/Back cover"      style="display: block; width: 100%; height: auto; margin: 0;"    >    <figcaption      class="image-caption"      style="            display: block;            width: 100%;            margin: 0.3rem 0 0;            padding: 0;            font-size: 0.72rem;            line-height: 1.25;            white-space: normal;            overflow-wrap: anywhere;            word-break: break-word;        "    >      圖二、SLUGGISH 封底/Back cover    </figcaption>  </figure></div><h2 id="慢慢滑比較快"><a href="#慢慢滑比較快" class="headerlink" title="慢慢滑比較快"></a>慢慢滑比較快</h2><p><ins><a href="https://www.merriam-webster.com/dictionary/sluggish"><em><strong>Sluggish</strong></em></a></ins> 的原意是緩慢、懶散、不急於前進。</p><blockquote><p><strong>慢慢滑，比較快</strong></p></blockquote><p><span id="sluggish-playlist"></span></p><h2 id="延伸聆聽"><a href="#延伸聆聽" class="headerlink" title="延伸聆聽"></a>延伸聆聽</h2><p>雜誌中提到的音樂播放清單可在這邊-&gt;<a href="https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLdmm5JmlECm0">🎧</a>收聽。</p>]]></content>
      
      
